Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Laadla (1994) Full Hindi Movie (4K) Sridevi & Anil Kapoor & Raveena | Farida Jalal | Bollywood Movie
snippet.description:
Laadla is a 1994 Indian Bollywood action drama film, directed by Raj Kanwar and produced by Nitin Manmohan. The film stars Anil Kapoor, Sridevi, and Raveena Tandon in pivotal roles. And Farida Jalal, Aruna Irani, Anupam Kher, Prem Chopra, Paresh Rawal, Mohnish Behl, Shakti Kapoor, Alok Nath, Arun Bakshi others in supportive role. It is known for its strong dialogues, emotional story and powerful performances.

The story revolves around Raju (Anil Kapoor), a hardworking and principled man who is hired by a ruthless and arrogant factory owner, Sheetal (Sridevi). Their personalities clash due to their different ideologies. Raju believes in honesty and humanity, while Sheetal believes in power and control. Their constant conflict leads to unexpected developments, including a dramatic marriage twist that changes their lives. 

लाडला (1994) एक भारतीय बॉलीवुड एक्शन-ड्रामा फिल्म है, जिसका निर्देशन राज कंवर ने किया है और निर्माण नितिन मनमोहन ने किया है। इस फिल्म में अनिल कपूर, श्रीदेवी और रवीना टंडन लीड रोल में हैं, तो वहीं फरीदा जलाल, अरुणा ईरानी, अनुपम खेर, प्रेम चोपड़ा, परेश रावल,मोहनीश बहल, शक्ति कपूर, आलोक नाथ और अरुण बख्शी सपोर्टिंव रोल में नजर आते हैं। 

कहानी एक ईमानदार और मेहनती आदमी राजू (अनिल कपूर) की है, जिसे एक घमंडी और सख्त फैक्ट्री मालकिन शीतल (श्रीदेवी) द्वारा काम पर रखा जाता है। राजू और शीतल की सोच में ज़मीन-आसमान का फर्क है। एक इंसानियत में विश्वास करता है, तो दूसरी ताकत और नियंत्रण में। उनके बीच का टकराव एक ऐसे मोड़ पर पहुंचता है, जहां एक अप्रत्याशित शादी उनके जीवन को बदल कर रख देती है।

snippet.title: Aarush Laila in ROAST MODE For 2 Hours |  @sadhikasehgal  | Aarush Laila Podcast | @aarushbhola17
snippet.description:
Aarush & Laila are BACK—and this time, it’s personal, hilarious, and completely unfiltered. From Delhi boys’ raw banter to deep friendship talks, this episode with host Sadhika Sehgal is packed with madness, emotion, and chaos.

They kick off by revisiting the prank they pulled on Manmansh Judeja, and quickly spiral into everything from acting gay, talking about virginity, to emotional revelations like Aarush buying his first house and the bond he shares with his dad, who Laila calls “the friend we never had.”

Expect savage birthday pranks (yes, the fake bike gift happened), awkward confessions (who Laila would date if he were gay), and brutal honesty about relationships - including why Aarush hates Laila’s girlfriend and thinks he deserves better. Aarush even exposes how Laila shares his live location with her 24/7, calling it toxic love at its peak.

You’ll hear wild stories of Laila almost getting arrested, calling his married ex while drunk, and getting slapped more than once, while Aarush remains surprisingly untouched by trouble. From gym talk to their very different music tastes, approaching girls at the gym, and even their gym playlists—nothing is off-limits. We also get a peek into their spiritual sides, with stories about Vrindavan trips, Lord Krishna, and Hanuman bhakti.

They spill tea on fake influencers, industry rivalry, and their Samay Raina’s India’s Got Latent Show experience.

They end with future dreams—Netflix series auditions, acting goals, their love languages, and the most chaotic Manali trip ever—think fire extinguishers, scared friends, and hotel staff complaints.

From friendship after 30, trusting each other with their girlfriends, to Delhi food recommendations and relationship red flags, this episode is a full ride - messy, meaningful, and made for everyone who’s ever had a best friend they can fight and laugh with at the same time.

AB de Villiers made his long-awaited return to cricket after four years in a thrilling WCL clash at Edgbaston 🏏 In a rain-hit 11-over match, South Africa Champions tied with West Indies Champions after both teams posted 80 runs. Lendl Simmons (28) & Chadwick Walton (27*) led the Windies effort, while JP Duminy’s late 25*(12) brought South Africa level. 💥

The drama continued with a bowl-out decider 🎯 SA Champions hit the stumps twice, while the Windies missed all four attempts as SA won the bowl-out 2–0 to clinch a thriller!
